  "title": "Re-usable Select Field Widget",
  "body": "Hey all, been working through this post (https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/issues/868) for a while now but not getting any where. Has anybody implemented a custom widget that creates a select field? My question is pretty much identical to this. \n\nI've read through both instantsearch docs and the helper docs but just not getting it. Can anyone guide me on creating this? The search form needs 6 select fields, each has 'all' a the top, must retain values so the user can then change options. \n\nAny help would be great!\n",
